      • GetHtmlFormattedHelp

        String GetHtmlFormattedHelp()
        returns html formatted help to guide users towards proper usage. Always include the following fields
        • Applies to - what policies types it applies to
        • Required and optional parameters
        • Description
        • State if this is processed as data comes in, or periodically (some aggregated data)
        Html is allowed, javascript is not
        Returns:
        Since:
        6.3
